cs.MA, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NI 

The paper deals with decision making in a distributed sensor network, which involves multiple agents making decisions based on incomplete information. This falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also addresses issues related to information gathering and processing, which are relevant to systems and control (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the application of the proposed method to sensor networks, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
